Class VirtualNetworkWaiters

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.oracle.bmc.core.VirtualNetworkWaiters

  • @Generated(value="OracleSDKGenerator",
           comments="API Version: 20160918")
public class VirtualNetworkWaiters
extends Object

    Collection of helper methods to produce Waiters for different resources of VirtualNetwork.

    The default configuration used is defined by Waiters#DEFAULT_POLLING_WAITER.
